EBC_Rwanda

As a network organisation, the European Business Chamber of Rwanda offers a range of services aimed at supporting its members.

Information

We gather and distribute key business information to our members, gathered by interviewing sector-specific experts and top government officials, and promptly distribute market studies, business intelligence, and policy updates.

Networking

EBCR features the biggest network of European-linked businesses in Rwanda. Our Members benefit from our exclusive members’ communication channel, as well as connections to key government officials and government agencies.

Advocacy

We leverage our network to voice our members’ concerns on key issues such as tax regime or civic relief funds and offer our Members the possibility to meet top government officials.
EBCR also talks in one voice for the European investors community.
